{{Infobox venue | name = Estadio Parque Maracaná | nickname = | logo_image = | logo_caption = | image = | caption = | fullname = | former_names = | location = [[Montevideo]], [[Uruguay]] | coordinates = {{Coord|34|50|12.47|S|56|10|16.63|W|scale:3125|display=inline,title}} | broke_ground = | built = | opened = {{Start date|2008|09|30}} | renovated = | expanded = | closed = | demolished = | owner = [[Club Sportivo Cerrito]] | operator = | surface = grass | scoreboard = | cost = | architect = | project_manager = | structural engineer = | services engineer = | general_contractor = | main_contractors = | capacity = 8,000 | suites = | record_attendance = | dimensions = | acreage = | tenants = [[Club Sportivo Cerrito]] | embedded = | website = <!-- {{URL|example.com}} --> }} The '''Estadio Parque Maracaná''' is a [[association football|football]] stadium in [[Casavalle]], [[Montevideo]], [[Uruguay]]. It has a capacity of 8,000 and is the home stadium of [[Club Sportivo Cerrito]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://int.soccerway.com/venues/uruguay/parque-maracana/|title=Parque Maracaná|publisher=Soccerway.com|accessdate=24 September 2011}}</ref> The stadium opened on Saturday 20 September 2008, with a match between Cerrito and [[Huracán Buceo]] in the [[Uruguayan Segunda División|Segunda División]] which Cerrito won 3 -0.
