The '''Tour of China''' is an annual professional [[road bicycle racing]] [[race stage|stage race]] held in [[China]] since 1995. The race is sanctioned by the International Cycling Union (UCI) as a 2.1 category race as part of the [[UCI Asia Tour]].

Since 2012, there are two parts of the Tour of China, '''Tour of China I''' and '''Tour of China II'''.

